data.description: The Annapolis floor plan is a spacious one-story home, perfect for smaller families looking for the perfect new home. The Annapolis provides 1,461 square feet with three bedrooms and two bathrooms. Mealtimes will be family times with a kitchen island for food prep, along with adjoining family and dining rooms. The laundry room is conveniently located next to the two-car garage, making it easy for night owls or early risers to do laundry without disturbing those sleeping. The owner's suite offers a walk-in closet and a double vanity perfect for those hectic weekday mornings. The Annapolis floor plan is a part of our new homes for sale in Sun City Center, stop by and find out more.
